{"tid":2338491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人唔要PS4 Pro可以讓比我","createTime":"2020-12-24T05:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T10:52:09.000Z","uid":181819,"like":2,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"75c6ace3128c985c6258cd236508f75b0bb11243","tid":2338491,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"利申左先 屋企冇乜錢買PS4<br />\n唔係話窮到穿窿 但就算有多餘錢都唔係去買PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買部PS4 Pro幾千蚊好似唔太貴 <br />\n但屋企唔太多錢 幾千蚊食到一個星期了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以睇下有冇巴絲有d全新/新淨ge二手PS4 Pro讓出黎 (只要Pro)<br />\n送比我就當然最好 但如果係平平地放比我我都唔介意嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位巴絲幫幫忙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果有野想交換可以問下我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝各位新年快樂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年願望除左香港回歸祖國外<br />\n其中一個細細地ge願望就係想自己有部打到FIFA既PS4 等自己生活冇咁頹廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259f1467cdb0886414adb3cd969696ffc52a44cb","tid":2338491,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"你搞好入台證我就讓俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入台證問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/892554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/892554</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a7df4d8fe0ad468c4a9b0ceb6518d6602103eeb","tid":2338491,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"無錢買部ps2囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5045cd7b9f51fbd58748a79e2b89bb80b0ca90a0","tid":2338491,"uid":18327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"reply